title: Twisted Sister - San Bernardino 1984.mkv
description:
DVD Twisted Sister 1984 Uncut Live At San Bernardino concert.

 Originally broadcast on MTV as the Stay Hungry Live concert, it had been commercially unavailable for years and previously unavailable as DVD. June 30, 2009 was the only day the DVD was available and only through participating, independent record stores with a limited stock.
